Interface DataDictionaryRegistryService

  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface DataDictionaryRegistryService
    This defines all the persistence layer API's for objects present in Data Dictionary(DCT).

      • createDataDictionary

        @Deprecated
String createDataDictionary(DataDictionary dictionary)
                                 throws DCTException
        Deprecated. 
        This API creates a data dictionary in persistent store and returns the unique identifier of stored DD. Name field in data dictionary is mandatory. The name of data dictionary is unique within the folder and hence in case of name collisions this api will throw exception. If identifier property is set in the Data Dictionary, it gets ignored by the api.
        Parameters:
        dictionary - data dictionary object
        Returns:
        id of data dictionary
        Throws:
        DCTException

      • updateDataDictionary

        @Deprecated
void updateDataDictionary(DataDictionary dictionary)
                               throws DCTException
        Deprecated. 
        This API updates an already existing data dictionary present in the system set with the same identifier. Name and Id fields in data dictionary are mandatory. The name of data dictionary is unique within the folder and hence in case of name collisions this api will throw exception.
        Parameters:
        dictionary - data dictionary object
        Throws:
        DCTException
